---
[v1] net: ethernet: mtk_eth_soc: change IB1 VLAN_TAG bit to IS_SP_TAG for NETSYSv3

In NETSYSv3, IB1 bit 18 is repurposed from VLAN_TAG to IS_SP_TAG
after the MTK_PPE_TB_CFG_IS_SP_TAG_EN is enabled. Rename
mtk_get_ib1_vlan_tag_mask() to mtk_get_ib1_sp_tag_mask() and update
its logic accordingly.
---
v1: Rename IB1 VLAN_TAG helper to IS_SP_TAG and restrict to NETSYSv3 or greater.
---

From 64d373fc955ef83dd69c645f9890c7d58250f929 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "chak-kei.lam" <chak-kei.lam@mediatek.com>
Date: Fri, 17 Apr 2026 11:05:55 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] net: ethernet: mtk_eth_soc: change IB1 VLAN_TAG bit to
 IS_SP_TAG for NETSYSv3

In NETSYSv3, IB1 bit 18 is repurposed from VLAN_TAG to IS_SP_TAG
after the MTK_PPE_TB_CFG_IS_SP_TAG_EN is enabled.

Rename mtk_get_ib1_vlan_tag_mask() to mtk_get_ib1_sp_tag_mask()
and update its logic to return MTK_FOE_IB1_BIND_IS_SP_TAG_V3 for
NETSYSv3 or greater, and 0 for older generations.
---
 drivers/net/ethernet/mediatek/mtk_eth_soc.h | 8 ++++----
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/mediatek/mtk_eth_soc.h
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/mediatek/mtk_eth_soc.h
@@ -1911,12 +1911,12 @@ static inline u32 mtk_get_ib1_ppoe_mask(
 	return MTK_FOE_IB1_BIND_PPPOE;
 }
 
-static inline u32 mtk_get_ib1_vlan_tag_mask(struct mtk_eth *eth)
+static inline u32 mtk_get_ib1_sp_tag_mask(struct mtk_eth *eth)
 {
-	if (mtk_is_netsys_v2_or_greater(eth))
-		return MTK_FOE_IB1_BIND_VLAN_TAG_V2;
+	if (mtk_is_netsys_v3_or_greater(eth))
+		return MTK_FOE_IB1_BIND_IS_SP_TAG_V3;
 
-	return MTK_FOE_IB1_BIND_VLAN_TAG;
+	return 0;
 }
 
 static inline u32 mtk_get_ib1_vlan_layer_mask(struct mtk_eth *eth)
